description: Top-level orchestrators — AgentRunner is the public API facade; RunOrchestrator is the central CQRS processor handling all bus messages.
files[2]{file,type,summary}:
  AgentRunner.php,final class,"The AgentRunner class orchestrates the lifecycle of agent execution runs by translating high-level inputs into discrete, idempotent steps. It manages state transitions for starting, continuing, steering, and canceling runs while ensuring reliable message dispatch via a command bus."
  RunOrchestrator.php,readonly final class,"The RunOrchestrator coordinates the lifecycle of an agent run by processing commands and handling step results through a reducer pattern. It manages state transitions, tool execution policies, and message hydration while persisting events and commands to their respective stores."
